# Mirror Gallery

Laravel 12 admin application for a glass/mirror workshop (orders, pieces, production stages, payments, warehouse).

## Stack

- PHP 8.2+, Laravel 12, PostgreSQL (`pgsql`)
- Backpack CRUD v6 + Backpack Pro, Tabler theme — all admin UI lives in Backpack
- Admin panel controllers: `app/Http/Controllers/Admin/*CrudController.php`
- Routes: `routes/backpack/` for admin, `routes/web.php` for public
- Frontend assets via Vite; Backpack assets via Basset

